long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Figure out what's important and actually do it.

I’ve used every project management tool there is over the years of building my own 7 figure brand and nothing comes close to the productivity i experience when i wake up early, make a small specific list of what things are actually important that day and start crossing things off.

Every time you open a new tab your list will be there, reminding you to focus on what’s important today.
